  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_8_7730-7768",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "7730-7768",
      "markText": "“我发现了一种极为精彩的证明方法，”费马补充道，“但是页边太窄，写不下了。”",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7730&rangeEnd=7768",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=7730&rangeEnd=7768"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_7_15589-15636",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "15589-15636",
      "markText": "在这个序列上方写下整数序列，你就得到了分数无穷和整数无穷的一一对应。所以，二者的数量是相同的！",
      "totalCount": 72,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15589&rangeEnd=15636",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=15589&rangeEnd=15636"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_12_3632-3724",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "3632-3724",
      "markText": "对应到餐厅的例子中，我们可以预料到，侍者会发誓说，坐在车厢两端的两位乘客在同一时刻点燃了餐后香烟；而站立在铁轨上向越过他的火车车窗张望的扳道工人则会坚持说，其中一位绅士首先点燃了香烟。",
      "totalCount": 54,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3632&rangeEnd=3724",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=3632&rangeEnd=3724"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_8_4693-4769",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "4693-4769",
      "markText": "不过，维诺格拉多夫的“四个质数”与哥德巴赫的“两个质数”之间的最后两步似乎是最艰难的两步，没有人知道证实或推翻这个困难的命题需要几年还是几个世纪的时间。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4693&rangeEnd=4769",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=4693&rangeEnd=4769"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_17_25638-25704",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "25638-25704",
      "markText": "当两种溶液放在一起时，核糖核酸分子开始以每束24个分子的方式结合，蛋白质分子开始缠绕在它们周围，形成实验开始时病毒颗粒的精确复制品。",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=25638&rangeEnd=25704",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=25638&rangeEnd=25704"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_7_21317-21474",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "21317-21474",
      "markText": "我们知道，☒表示所有整数的数量，☒1表示所有几何点的数量，☒2表示所有曲线的数量，但是还没有人想到应该用☒3描述的明确的无穷对象集合。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=21317&rangeEnd=21474",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=21317&rangeEnd=21474"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_10_880-931",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "880-931",
      "markText": "这里应该补充一点：三个坐标不一定都是表示某种距离的数字。实际上，在某些情况下，使用角度作坐标更加方便。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=880&rangeEnd=931",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=880&rangeEnd=931"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_8_829-881",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "829-881",
      "markText": "虽然数学喜欢保持纯粹，远离其他科学，但是以物理学为代表的其他科学却很喜欢数学，试图尽可能地与数学扯上关系",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=829&rangeEnd=881",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=829&rangeEnd=881"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_16_35680-35734",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "35680-35734",
      "markText": "所有依赖于分子不规则热运动的物理过程都在朝着概率增加的方向前进。当一切归于平静时，平衡的状态对应于最大概率。",
      "totalCount": 33,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=35680&rangeEnd=35734",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=35680&rangeEnd=35734"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_7_765-973",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "765-973",
      "markText": "力水平表现堪忧，这个故事可能只是一种恶意污蔑",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=765&rangeEnd=973",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=765&rangeEnd=973"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_7_5257-5295",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "5257-5295",
      "markText": "他需要向西萨提供18,446,744,073,709,551,615个麦粒！",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5257&rangeEnd=5295",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=5257&rangeEnd=5295"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_7_6536-6597",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "6536-6597",
      "markText": "因此，舍罕王欠了总理大臣很大一笔财富。他有两个选择，一是接受总理大臣持续不断的要求，二是砍下他的头。我们怀疑他选择了后者。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6536&rangeEnd=6597",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=6536&rangeEnd=6597"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_7_14104-14135",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14104-14135",
      "markText": "现在，所有奇数号房间都空了，无穷个新顾客可以轻松地入住酒店了。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14104&rangeEnd=14135",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14104&rangeEnd=14135"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_8_3288-3490",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "3288-3490",
      "markText": "德国数学家欧拉（Euler）指出，这个序列第五个数+1的结果4,294,967,297不是质数，而是6,700,417和641的乘积。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3288&rangeEnd=3490",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=3288&rangeEnd=3490"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_10_7932-7945",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "7932-7945",
      "markText": "于是完成了欧拉公式的证明。",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26401373&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7932&rangeEnd=7945",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/24b32b307192da5d24b419f?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=7932&rangeEnd=7945"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26401373_10_17833-17874",
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "range": "17833-17874",
